Twitter metric System
  The application calculates the twitter score based on Popularity and activeness of a particular user.
This application is to calculate the twitt
er score of a particular user on the basis of Popu
larity, Activeness,etc. The factors that contribut
e to the score are as follows:
1) No of Followers
2) No of Followings
3) No of retweets
4) Recency of Tweets
5) No of Tweets